WEBVTT

01:39.560 --> 01:43.270
[Road to Success]

01:44.690 --> 01:47.850
[Episode 28]

01:49.120 --> 01:50.680
Long time no see, Ms. Lin.

01:52.009 --> 01:53.009
Director Qian.

01:53.030 --> 01:55.160
I must apologize to you and the school.

01:56.080 --> 01:57.990
If the school decides to discipline me,

01:57.990 --> 02:00.250
I will accept whatever decision is made.

02:01.510 --> 02:03.210
Actually, according to
the school's regulations,

02:03.210 --> 02:04.720
being absent from work for 3 days

02:04.720 --> 02:06.180
is grounds for dismissal.

02:06.590 --> 02:07.450
Director Qian.

02:07.720 --> 02:09.050
I don't have to return to my post,

02:09.050 --> 02:10.120
but please allow me

02:10.120 --> 02:12.800
to continue serving as
the football team supervisor.

02:12.800 --> 02:14.230
I'm willing to work for free.

02:14.230 --> 02:15.600
How is that possible?

02:15.620 --> 02:17.160
Think about it, how could the school

02:17.160 --> 02:19.070
hire someone
who isn't a teacher at the school

02:19.070 --> 02:20.600
to serve as the supervisor?

02:22.570 --> 02:23.620
However,

02:24.960 --> 02:26.690
you didn't actually skip work.

02:27.120 --> 02:28.579
You filed a leave request.

02:32.110 --> 02:32.680
Right, right.

02:32.680 --> 02:33.310
Here.

02:33.440 --> 02:34.200
Look,

02:34.470 --> 02:35.470
I even signed it.

02:34.970 --> 02:35.510
[Request for Leave for Teachers of
Hongjing No. 8 High]

02:35.530 --> 02:36.329
[Dear Director, I'm writing to request
19 days of leave due to health issues.]

02:36.350 --> 02:36.900
[I kindly ask for your approval.
Thank you.]

02:36.910 --> 02:37.650
[Person Covering Duties: Wang Fa]
[Applicant: Lin Wanxing]

02:38.230 --> 02:39.070
Wang Fa...

02:40.840 --> 02:42.680
Having a family member fill out
the leave request for you

02:42.680 --> 02:44.940
isn't a serious violation of principle.

02:45.620 --> 02:46.870
Ms. Lin.

02:46.930 --> 02:48.370
Just go back to work

02:48.400 --> 02:49.850
once you recover.

02:54.240 --> 02:55.700
Thank you, Director Qian.

03:02.190 --> 03:04.430
[Dear Director Qian. With the exams
approaching, the team urgently needs...]

03:07.520 --> 03:09.400
So Qian also reads poems?

03:07.570 --> 03:08.370
[If I can stop one heart from breaking,]

03:08.390 --> 03:09.560
[I shall not live in vain.]

03:17.960 --> 03:18.840
Director Qian.

03:19.680 --> 03:22.640
Can I borrow a book from you?

03:23.840 --> 03:24.750
A book?

03:25.079 --> 03:26.079
What book?

03:28.760 --> 03:30.620
That red poetry collection.

03:36.710 --> 03:37.400
Sure.

03:37.910 --> 03:39.680
I'm all for

03:39.680 --> 03:41.010
young people reading.

03:41.290 --> 03:42.050
Here you are.

03:41.690 --> 03:42.750
[The Complete Poems of Emily Dickinson]

03:44.840 --> 03:45.680
Thank you.

03:52.960 --> 03:54.360
It's so nice

03:54.360 --> 03:55.640
to have Ms. Lin back.

03:55.940 --> 03:57.800
Even this cucumber tastes sweet.

03:57.910 --> 04:00.110
I wonder what Ms. Lin wants to see us for.

04:00.280 --> 04:01.120
Guys.

04:01.400 --> 04:02.520
Ms. Lin.

04:02.840 --> 04:04.170
Thank you for the fruit.

04:04.910 --> 04:06.800
I just went to Director Qian's office

04:06.800 --> 04:08.840
and borrowed a poetry collection from him.

04:08.840 --> 04:09.710
Look.

04:09.710 --> 04:11.180
There's a dog-eared corner on this page

04:11.180 --> 04:12.640
of the poetry collection.

04:13.230 --> 04:13.640
[If I can stop one heart from breaking,]

04:13.660 --> 04:14.070
[I shall not live in vain.]

04:14.820 --> 04:16.589
This looks familiar.

04:17.120 --> 04:19.600
Isn't this the poem from the fax?

04:17.930 --> 04:18.610
[If I can ease one life the aching,]

04:18.630 --> 04:19.430
[or cool one pain,]

04:22.070 --> 04:24.070
So the mystery person is Qian?

04:28.420 --> 04:29.750
But that can't be right.

04:29.790 --> 04:31.390
The writing on my football lending card

04:31.390 --> 04:32.430
was handwritten,

04:32.430 --> 04:34.510
and it doesn't match his handwriting.

04:34.510 --> 04:36.170
I was thinking about that too.

04:40.390 --> 04:42.120
Let's go over everything
from the beginning together.

04:42.120 --> 04:43.510
First,

04:43.510 --> 04:46.280
we found the football lending card
in Chen Jianghe's desk drawer,

04:46.280 --> 04:48.180
then the crossword puzzle

04:48.200 --> 04:49.960
in Qin Ao's desk drawer.

04:49.990 --> 04:51.840
And finally

04:51.860 --> 04:53.320
that map in my desk drawer.

04:55.690 --> 04:57.700
So these clues prove

04:58.159 --> 04:59.560
that whoever wrote the note
on the football lending card

04:59.560 --> 05:00.870
must know us very well.

05:03.160 --> 05:04.480
I agree.

05:07.830 --> 05:09.830
But who could it be?

05:14.930 --> 05:16.490
I think

05:17.430 --> 05:19.160
I may have figured out who it is.

05:22.310 --> 05:25.070
I'm going to go ask Director Qian
for a straight answer.

05:25.070 --> 05:26.000
Do you guys know

05:26.000 --> 05:28.380
where he usually goes after school?

05:29.070 --> 05:30.360
To Hongyang Park to play chess.

05:30.360 --> 05:32.220
Rain or shine, he never misses it.

05:35.360 --> 05:36.040
Check.

05:40.000 --> 05:41.680
-Corner knight check.
-Grandma, look.

05:41.680 --> 05:43.610
-I know how to ride it.
-Be careful.

05:43.630 --> 05:45.950
Darn it, a corner knight check followed by
a cannon.

05:45.950 --> 05:46.720
Unbeatable.

05:46.720 --> 05:47.390
You're done for.

05:47.390 --> 05:48.240
I'm done playing with you.

05:48.240 --> 05:49.950
I'm going home
to take care of my grandson.

05:49.950 --> 05:50.630
I'm done playing with you.

05:50.630 --> 05:51.630
You're running off after just one game?

05:51.630 --> 05:52.890
You still owe me a meal.

05:53.480 --> 05:54.940
Let's continue tomorrow.

05:57.310 --> 05:58.310
Ms. Lin.

05:59.260 --> 06:00.120
Director Qian.

06:00.560 --> 06:01.930
Let me play

06:01.970 --> 06:03.330
this game with you.

06:03.360 --> 06:04.880
That would be great.

06:04.900 --> 06:05.510
Come on.

06:12.310 --> 06:13.040
You go first.

06:19.720 --> 06:20.630
Knight jump.

06:23.430 --> 06:25.390
Did you come to see me
about something, Ms. Lin?

06:25.390 --> 06:26.390
Director Qian.

06:27.240 --> 06:28.750
Thank you

06:29.720 --> 06:30.720
for everything.

06:31.220 --> 06:32.100
Thank me?

06:32.120 --> 06:33.930
I haven't done anything to deserve it.

06:33.930 --> 06:35.630
If you have something to say, just say it.

06:35.630 --> 06:37.680
Letting me come to work at Hongjing

06:37.770 --> 06:39.390
and become the football team supervisor,

06:39.390 --> 06:41.320
helping the team get reorganized—

06:41.390 --> 06:45.600
which one of these things wasn't something
you helped with behind the scenes?

06:45.600 --> 06:46.670
Am I right?

06:49.240 --> 06:50.520
Elaborate on that.

06:53.790 --> 06:56.040
Stuffing a colorful box
filled with puzzles

06:56.040 --> 06:57.640
into a student's desk drawer

06:57.680 --> 06:59.340
without fear of being caught—

06:59.680 --> 07:02.750
that must have been done
by someone with a classroom key.

07:02.750 --> 07:03.510
There aren't many people

07:03.510 --> 07:05.640
who have keys to multiple classrooms,

07:06.230 --> 07:07.490
but you're one of them.

07:09.160 --> 07:09.990
Go on.

07:11.700 --> 07:14.030
One of the puzzles was a crossword puzzle,

07:14.280 --> 07:16.200
which happens to be your interest

07:16.230 --> 07:17.990
and something you're best at.

07:22.240 --> 07:24.190
"If I can stop one heart

07:24.190 --> 07:25.830
from breaking..."

07:26.660 --> 07:28.290
It was precisely this poem

07:29.310 --> 07:30.750
that convinced me

07:31.430 --> 07:33.030
you were the mystery person.

07:36.720 --> 07:37.680
Today,

07:38.820 --> 07:41.430
when you asked to
borrow that poetry collection,

07:41.430 --> 07:42.870
I already knew.

07:48.050 --> 07:50.010
Knowing the students inside and out

07:50.010 --> 07:51.740
wouldn't be difficult for you.

07:52.190 --> 07:54.700
But the mystery person knows me
to a degree

07:55.240 --> 07:57.300
that you couldn't possibly achieve.

07:58.430 --> 07:59.750
So I guess

08:02.470 --> 08:04.600
there's more than one mystery person.

08:07.480 --> 08:08.680
There's another one.

08:10.370 --> 08:11.980
Could it be my grandpa?

08:18.630 --> 08:20.360
You're just like your grandpa—

08:21.330 --> 08:23.750
playing chess to mess with
my train of thought.

08:23.750 --> 08:25.210
That's unsportsmanlike.

08:25.880 --> 08:27.460
That makes sense then.

08:29.330 --> 08:30.930
But I have one more question.

08:31.630 --> 08:33.480
Only internal staff can register for

08:33.480 --> 08:35.630
an email account at Hengjiu.

08:36.480 --> 08:37.150
So...

08:41.039 --> 08:43.070
Have you ever heard the boys

08:43.480 --> 08:45.940
talk about Coach Jiang
of the football team?

08:46.340 --> 08:47.520
Of course I have.

08:50.710 --> 08:52.780
Jiang had a son named Jiang Xun.

08:53.570 --> 08:54.770
He works at Hengjiu

08:55.490 --> 08:58.490
as the general manager's
administrative assistant.

08:58.790 --> 09:01.150
After Jiang passed away
due to an accident,

09:01.150 --> 09:04.590
he put all the pieces together
and figured out what had happened.

09:04.590 --> 09:05.480
This Jiang Xun

09:05.480 --> 09:07.940
was your grandfather's favorite disciple.

09:08.140 --> 09:09.990
While your grandfather was in hospital,

09:09.990 --> 09:12.230
he often went to visit him.

09:12.930 --> 09:14.260
Wanxing...

09:14.290 --> 09:16.480
When Wanxing was 5 or 6,

09:16.500 --> 09:17.500
she

09:17.550 --> 09:18.550
asked me all the time,

09:18.550 --> 09:23.670
"Grandpa, why is my name Wanxing
and not something about the moon?"

09:23.670 --> 09:25.030
I said, "Wanxing,

09:25.030 --> 09:26.080
there are many stars,

09:26.080 --> 09:27.640
but only one moon."

09:27.670 --> 09:29.270
She said she wanted to be the moon.

09:29.270 --> 09:31.320
I told her it was better to be a star.

09:33.480 --> 09:34.080
Darling.

09:34.840 --> 09:35.270
Here.

09:35.270 --> 09:36.720
I forgot to tell you.

09:36.720 --> 09:38.200
I don't feel like eating.

09:39.060 --> 09:40.150
Then you eat it.

09:40.150 --> 09:40.670
What?

09:40.670 --> 09:41.200
I...

09:41.600 --> 09:42.440
It's delicious.

09:42.440 --> 09:42.910
Come on,

09:43.070 --> 09:44.140
take it. Come on.

09:45.990 --> 09:47.270
Jiang Xun.

09:47.550 --> 09:49.280
Thank you for coming to see me

09:49.550 --> 09:51.810
and listening to me ramble on for so long.

09:52.320 --> 09:53.270
Pardon me.

09:53.270 --> 09:53.960
Pardon me.

09:53.960 --> 09:55.200
I'm your student.

09:55.840 --> 09:57.200
It's only natural.

09:57.840 --> 09:59.090
Actually, the one

09:59.280 --> 10:02.240
he's most worried about is Wanxing.

10:03.200 --> 10:04.550
Don't worry.

10:04.550 --> 10:06.150
Wanxing is such an outstanding person.

10:06.150 --> 10:07.320
She'll be fine.

10:13.340 --> 10:14.620
Time truly flies.

10:15.490 --> 10:18.550
It's already been a year
since your father passed away.

10:19.550 --> 10:21.000
If I could see him,

10:21.000 --> 10:23.080
I'd tell Jiang

10:23.080 --> 10:25.960
that he had a wonderful son.

10:26.250 --> 10:28.160
You have to thank me, you know?

10:30.240 --> 10:31.710
Sure. Thank you.

10:33.840 --> 10:35.440
Your grandpa and grandma

10:35.440 --> 10:37.720
wanted you to get back on your feet,

10:38.670 --> 10:40.200
while Jiang Xun

10:40.200 --> 10:42.420
wanted to carry on his father's legacy

10:42.440 --> 10:44.560
to keep the football team going.

10:45.440 --> 10:47.370
The two of them hit it off right away

10:47.450 --> 10:50.570
and came up with
the "mystery person" plan.

10:50.670 --> 10:52.550
We've made a decision.

10:52.550 --> 10:53.740
You carry it out.

10:54.320 --> 10:58.080
-God, the first step is the probate.
-The plan was missing an executor,

10:58.080 --> 10:59.270
so they asked me

10:59.600 --> 11:01.270
to take on that role.

11:01.600 --> 11:02.840
-It's "work hard."
-Oh, it's "work hard."

11:02.840 --> 11:04.270
Look at the way you wrote "hard."

11:04.090 --> 11:08.420
[Action Plan]

11:04.270 --> 11:08.720
Have Wanxing teach at Hongjing No. 8 High.

11:08.720 --> 11:09.320
Great. Applause.

11:09.320 --> 11:10.440
Great.

11:11.520 --> 11:13.580
[Wanxing, I'll be gone soon.]

11:14.480 --> 11:16.070
The first step of the plan

11:17.030 --> 11:19.360
was for your grandpa
to write you a letter,

11:19.440 --> 11:22.570
suggesting that you come to teach
at Hongjing No. 8 High.

11:22.620 --> 11:24.510
[Remember to eat well and live well.]

11:24.440 --> 11:25.600
And that letter

11:25.720 --> 11:27.670
set our mysterious plan in motion.

11:28.790 --> 11:29.670
First,

11:30.360 --> 11:31.960
it was to bring you
to Hongjing No. 8 High,

11:31.960 --> 11:34.820
so that the football team
could have a new backbone.

11:35.840 --> 11:36.670
Second,

11:37.270 --> 11:39.880
it was to help you
become part of the football team,

11:39.880 --> 11:43.080
so that you and the boys
could support and save each other.

11:47.200 --> 11:47.790
Look.

11:47.790 --> 11:48.590
This would do.

11:56.440 --> 11:58.630
First, that 100-time football lending card

11:58.630 --> 12:01.430
was meant to spark your curiosity
about football.

12:03.910 --> 12:04.670
Wonderful.

12:05.840 --> 12:07.360
"Start over from the beginning"—

12:07.360 --> 12:08.080
does this work?

12:08.080 --> 12:08.910
It needs to be more positive.

12:08.910 --> 12:09.840
"Dare to be the first."

12:09.840 --> 12:13.550
-Leave the kids some room for imagination.
-That's right.

12:13.840 --> 12:15.300
Cross it out. Cross it out.

12:15.580 --> 12:16.670
Second,

12:15.700 --> 12:20.120
[Make a great coup]

12:16.670 --> 12:18.230
the crossword puzzle

12:18.550 --> 12:20.910
was meant to give you a new understanding
of the football team.

12:20.910 --> 12:21.960
Let it dry a bit.

12:21.960 --> 12:23.000
Put it here.

12:27.980 --> 12:31.650
[Calculate the value of
Euler's totient function]

12:31.700 --> 12:34.030
[Calculate]

12:31.910 --> 12:34.200
The third was that mysterious map.

12:34.240 --> 12:36.500
It was meant to help you and the kids

12:36.530 --> 12:37.980
find a new home.

12:44.360 --> 12:45.890
Just take this place and...

12:46.080 --> 12:47.200
This...

12:52.740 --> 12:53.510
[Wanxing, I'll be gone soon. It's a shame]

12:53.530 --> 12:54.230
[we didn't get to see each other
one last time.]

12:58.380 --> 13:06.610
[Lin Xunya]

13:22.550 --> 13:26.510
Jiang and your grandfather both
passed away with unfulfilled concerns.

13:26.510 --> 13:27.360
So of course, Jiang Xun and I

13:27.360 --> 13:29.550
wanted to carry on with this

13:29.550 --> 13:31.440
and fulfill their final wishes—

13:32.080 --> 13:34.670
to let the lost Wanxing
and the helpless kids

13:35.350 --> 13:36.820
illuminate each other.

13:40.840 --> 13:42.320
I think as for Coach Wang,

13:42.320 --> 13:43.960
it was indeed an accident.

13:44.480 --> 13:45.670
But I still believe

13:46.360 --> 13:48.840
it was precisely because
you're such a nice person

13:48.840 --> 13:49.480
that God

13:49.480 --> 13:52.180
placed Wang Fa in this difficult chapter

13:52.260 --> 13:53.620
of your life.

14:01.400 --> 14:02.900
And finally, he told me

14:03.960 --> 14:05.870
that once you discovered the truth,

14:05.870 --> 14:08.470
there would be one final gift
for me to give you.

14:10.480 --> 14:11.600
He hoped to tell you

14:12.910 --> 14:14.780
about it himself

14:14.810 --> 14:16.120
in a happy place.

14:17.440 --> 14:18.200
Of course,

14:18.570 --> 14:21.700
Jiang Xun also had something
he wanted to say to the kids.

14:35.080 --> 14:36.550
Kids,

14:38.910 --> 14:40.080
I'm sorry.

14:41.480 --> 14:43.550
Your old man Jiang here

14:44.360 --> 14:45.320
has to...

14:46.030 --> 14:48.240
Has to break his promise.

14:49.470 --> 14:51.590
I promised

14:52.670 --> 14:56.550
I'd lead you to win the championship.

14:57.920 --> 14:59.350
But I...

15:01.320 --> 15:03.480
I won't be able to do it.

15:04.270 --> 15:06.360
I feel very guilty.

15:08.320 --> 15:10.150
In my heart,

15:11.030 --> 15:12.080
you guys

15:13.360 --> 15:16.230
have been champions all along.

15:17.550 --> 15:20.080
Fu Xinshu,

15:21.800 --> 15:23.800
Yu Ming,

15:27.190 --> 15:29.400
Zhi Hui,

15:32.430 --> 15:33.960
Zheng Ren,

15:34.600 --> 15:36.220
and...

15:36.670 --> 15:38.800
Zheng Feiyang,

15:40.970 --> 15:42.760
Qi Liang,

15:45.650 --> 15:47.340
Lin Lu,

15:48.750 --> 15:50.200
Qin Ao,

15:52.960 --> 15:55.320
Chen Jianghe,

15:57.720 --> 15:59.720
Feng Suo,

16:01.240 --> 16:03.670
and Jiang Tianyu.

16:04.840 --> 16:07.270
I will remember

16:07.270 --> 16:10.270
every single one of you.

16:11.790 --> 16:13.670
I hope

16:13.670 --> 16:15.550
that even without me,

16:16.310 --> 16:17.780
you guys...

16:18.930 --> 16:20.520
You guys will still

16:21.480 --> 16:23.080
continue to

16:23.910 --> 16:26.870
love football.

16:29.200 --> 16:31.030
Kids,

16:34.200 --> 16:35.200
good...

16:37.080 --> 16:37.960
Good...

16:40.440 --> 16:43.080
Goodbye.

16:44.600 --> 16:47.550
Goodbye.

16:52.150 --> 16:55.320
Goodbye.

17:07.380 --> 17:08.510
Hello, guys.

17:08.640 --> 17:11.680
I'm Jiang Xun, Coach Jiang's son.

17:13.109 --> 17:15.510
A little over 2 years ago—

17:16.069 --> 17:17.069
right around the time you guys

17:17.069 --> 17:18.730
first started at Hongjing No.8 High—

17:18.730 --> 17:20.260
my dad fell seriously ill.

17:20.290 --> 17:22.160
He remained unconscious for a long time,

17:22.160 --> 17:25.359
so I took him to Yongchuan,
where I worked, for treatment.

17:25.750 --> 17:26.640
During his time

17:26.640 --> 17:28.079
in the ICU,

17:28.290 --> 17:30.220
he never regained consciousness.

17:31.470 --> 17:34.390
Then, on the morning of
the day he passed away,

17:34.510 --> 17:36.720
he suddenly opened his eyes and told me

17:37.090 --> 17:39.150
he wanted to record a message for you.

17:40.940 --> 17:42.790
Which is the one you just saw.

17:45.310 --> 17:46.910
What I want to tell you is

17:48.790 --> 17:50.050
that your Coach Jiang,

17:51.270 --> 17:53.930
even during those days
when he was unconscious,

17:54.280 --> 17:56.610
never once thought about giving up on you.

18:14.790 --> 18:15.590
Is it all set?

18:18.110 --> 18:18.920
Wanxing.

18:20.350 --> 18:23.510
How's your life been going
at No. 8 High School?

18:24.270 --> 18:26.270
Have those kids on the football team

18:26.270 --> 18:28.550
been bothering you so much that

18:28.550 --> 18:31.070
you've had no time to think about me?

18:33.510 --> 18:35.270
I'm very happy.

18:36.270 --> 18:37.510
I know

18:38.070 --> 18:40.000
it might not be long—

18:40.590 --> 18:43.310
maybe just 3 months,

18:43.880 --> 18:45.440
or maybe longer.

18:46.270 --> 18:48.510
But I just know

18:48.510 --> 18:51.440
that you'll definitely see this video.

18:56.310 --> 18:59.160
You've been through a lot lately.

18:58.380 --> 19:04.060
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

19:00.700 --> 19:02.150
I believe

19:02.260 --> 19:04.740
you're definitely able to

19:04.650 --> 19:09.180
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

19:04.760 --> 19:06.930
eat well

19:06.960 --> 19:09.030
and live well.

19:10.310 --> 19:11.590
Are you

19:11.260 --> 19:16.360
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

19:12.480 --> 19:14.730
able to smile

19:14.750 --> 19:16.420
more often now?

19:17.190 --> 19:22.620
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

19:21.430 --> 19:22.350
Wanxing.

19:23.030 --> 19:24.050
In the future,

19:24.190 --> 19:29.900
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

19:24.240 --> 19:27.790
there will be many times
when you feel lost and unsure.

19:28.510 --> 19:30.550
But I believe

19:30.640 --> 19:35.440
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

19:31.000 --> 19:32.920
that you know.

19:33.510 --> 19:35.880
You know that I love you.

19:36.550 --> 19:38.590
I've always been here,

19:37.110 --> 19:42.260
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

19:39.720 --> 19:41.510
and I always will be.

19:42.370 --> 19:46.280
I'm just staying by your side
in a different way now.

19:43.240 --> 19:48.410
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

19:49.260 --> 19:55.150
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

19:55.870 --> 20:01.640
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

20:02.320 --> 20:07.930
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

20:05.310 --> 20:06.550
Turns out Coach Jiang

20:07.750 --> 20:09.400
never gave up on us.

20:08.780 --> 20:14.020
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

20:10.270 --> 20:11.830
For Coach Jiang

20:12.790 --> 20:14.880
and Ms. Lin's grandparents,

20:15.080 --> 20:20.660
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

20:16.790 --> 20:18.310
we must win.

20:21.400 --> 20:27.140
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

20:27.920 --> 20:33.980
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

20:34.580 --> 20:40.280
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

20:43.620 --> 20:44.900
Alright, gather the balls.

20:44.900 --> 20:45.550
Get ready to run.

20:45.550 --> 20:46.160
Okay.

20:46.160 --> 20:47.380
-It's her.
-It's her.

20:47.400 --> 20:48.000
It's her.

20:48.000 --> 20:49.510
So it's her.

20:52.110 --> 20:54.840
Yeah, I wouldn't have known
if you didn't tell me.

20:56.110 --> 20:57.030
She's such a homewrecker.

20:57.030 --> 20:58.960
-So it was her you were talking about?
-Yeah, it's her.

20:58.960 --> 20:59.720
-What was that?
-Shut up!

20:59.720 --> 21:00.270
What do you want?

21:00.270 --> 21:00.920
-What's wrong with you?
-Shut up!

21:00.920 --> 21:01.510
What are you looking at?

21:01.510 --> 21:02.240
-What do you think you're doing?
-Alright, alright.

21:02.240 --> 21:03.160
Anything you want to say?

21:03.160 --> 21:04.690
-Let's go.
-Yeah, let's go.

21:05.140 --> 21:06.010
Ms. Lin,

21:06.040 --> 21:06.930
ignore them.

21:07.580 --> 21:08.410
I'm okay.

21:11.510 --> 21:12.370
Go run.

21:14.600 --> 21:15.130
Let's go.

21:20.790 --> 21:21.520
Are you okay?

21:23.730 --> 21:25.300
After all this time,

21:25.330 --> 21:26.990
I've come to understand this:

21:27.160 --> 21:29.450
the rumors won't stop.

21:29.850 --> 21:31.850
But until the truth comes to light,

21:32.250 --> 21:34.380
I need to learn to stop blaming myself.

22:01.540 --> 22:02.340
You mean

22:03.300 --> 22:05.560
you had guessed it was Xiang Zi all along?

22:07.010 --> 22:09.150
I never tried to verify it.

22:10.100 --> 22:11.130
Before,

22:12.240 --> 22:14.500
I didn't even have the courage to face it.

22:16.160 --> 22:18.960
There were two pieces of evidence
used to frame me.

22:19.710 --> 22:21.750
When Professor Shu committed suicide,

22:21.750 --> 22:24.410
there was a photo from my trip
tucked in his book.

22:25.610 --> 22:26.960
Director Jia from the department

22:26.960 --> 22:28.590
also used that very photo

22:29.040 --> 22:31.770
to question my relationship
with Professor Shu.

22:31.830 --> 22:33.130
I had many copies of that set of photos

22:33.130 --> 22:34.610
printed back then.

22:34.890 --> 22:35.890
I guess

22:36.990 --> 22:40.790
the one they found was taken from
those copies without my knowledge.

22:40.800 --> 22:41.590
Then,

22:44.110 --> 22:45.710
what was the other evidence?

22:51.860 --> 22:55.860
It was a video supposedly showing
me going to Professor Shu's hotel room

22:56.540 --> 22:59.540
during the
China Psychological Research Symposium.

23:00.550 --> 23:02.210
Hotel surveillance footage?

23:02.580 --> 23:04.510
The person in that video wasn't me,

23:06.220 --> 23:08.020
but they were dressed and styled

23:08.580 --> 23:10.300
exactly like I was.

23:10.840 --> 23:12.320
No matter how I argued,

23:12.340 --> 23:13.940
they wouldn't believe me,

23:13.970 --> 23:18.500
and they said my attempts to defend myself
only made me look even more suspicious.

23:19.050 --> 23:20.640
Do you still have

23:21.750 --> 23:22.550
that video?

23:26.200 --> 23:27.680
After it happened,

23:28.880 --> 23:31.140
I tried to ask the hotel for that footage.

23:31.240 --> 23:32.110
They told me

23:32.880 --> 23:35.340
the surveillance footage
had already been overwritten,

23:35.340 --> 23:36.960
and that they couldn't let me have it

23:36.960 --> 23:38.330
due to guest privacy.

23:44.320 --> 23:45.700
Hotel surveillance footage

23:45.700 --> 23:47.420
couldn't possibly have been overwritten
that quickly.

23:47.420 --> 23:49.020
There must be more to this.

23:51.040 --> 23:52.280
Besides the hotel,

23:52.670 --> 23:53.600
was that video

23:53.990 --> 23:55.520
circulated anywhere else?

24:00.720 --> 24:02.420
It circulated on the school forum

24:02.420 --> 24:03.830
for a while back then,

24:04.750 --> 24:06.950
but the original post has been deleted.

24:16.310 --> 24:17.040
Don't worry.

24:18.550 --> 24:20.810
We'll find the original source somehow.

24:21.550 --> 24:23.150
We'll figure something out.

24:28.130 --> 24:28.890
Back then,

24:29.170 --> 24:31.200
I was trapped in a struggle
to prove my innocence.

24:31.200 --> 24:31.810
This time,

24:32.470 --> 24:33.890
I'll uncover the truth

24:33.090 --> 24:34.280
[Director Jia]

24:34.380 --> 24:35.440
and reclaim the justice
that was taken from me.

24:34.430 --> 24:37.470
[Hello, Director Jia.]

24:37.630 --> 24:39.100
Hello, Director Jia.

24:39.320 --> 24:40.530
This is Lin Wanxing.

24:41.540 --> 24:43.910
I'd like to ask you about something

24:41.680 --> 24:44.120
[Director Jia]

24:43.950 --> 24:45.810
concerning that previous video.

24:55.750 --> 24:56.240
Coach.

24:56.240 --> 24:57.070
Ms. Lin.

24:57.400 --> 24:58.550
We're here to deliver food.

24:58.550 --> 24:59.350
So early?

24:59.350 --> 25:01.070
Isn't your class in the evening?

25:01.070 --> 25:03.680
We just wanted to see
if there's anything we can do to help.

25:03.680 --> 25:04.270
We just received the video

25:04.270 --> 25:06.160
that was used to frame Ms. Lin back then.

25:06.160 --> 25:08.070
We're trying to see
if we can find any flaws.

25:08.070 --> 25:09.310
Really? Let's do it together then.

25:09.310 --> 25:10.640
Many hands make light work.

25:10.640 --> 25:11.440
That's right.

25:21.880 --> 25:22.600
Ms. Lin,

25:22.630 --> 25:23.430
this...

25:23.680 --> 25:25.500
Although that person dressed like me,

25:25.500 --> 25:26.920
it really wasn't me.

25:26.950 --> 25:28.380
Xiang Zi knows you very well,

25:28.380 --> 25:30.060
so it wouldn't be difficult for him
to impersonate you.

25:30.060 --> 25:31.340
But this video alone

25:31.360 --> 25:33.090
isn't enough to prove
that the person in it was Xiang Zi.

25:33.090 --> 25:34.140
There must be some inconsistency.

25:34.140 --> 25:35.270
Let's keep looking.

25:45.410 --> 25:46.170
Look.

25:52.270 --> 25:52.960
Before going in,

25:52.960 --> 25:54.480
did he turn his neck left and right

25:54.480 --> 25:55.400
and then pat it?

25:55.420 --> 25:56.310
Indeed.

25:56.940 --> 25:58.130
If you don't look closely,

25:58.130 --> 25:59.820
you'd think he was fixing his hair.

25:59.820 --> 26:00.640
And because he had long hair,

26:00.640 --> 26:01.700
it wasn't obvious.

26:01.750 --> 26:02.580
It's him.

26:02.580 --> 26:06.450
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

26:02.600 --> 26:04.310
That's one of his habitual gestures.

26:04.310 --> 26:06.590
He does this whenever he gets nervous.

26:06.610 --> 26:07.920
Then what are we waiting for?

26:07.920 --> 26:08.790
Let's just have the police arrest him.

26:08.790 --> 26:09.320
Exactly.

26:10.650 --> 26:12.240
But a mere habitual gesture

26:12.270 --> 26:14.200
isn't enough to serve as evidence.

26:16.110 --> 26:17.550
Then what should we do next?

26:17.550 --> 26:19.350
How do we collect more evidence?

26:21.330 --> 26:22.260
Let me have a try.

26:22.720 --> 26:23.640
I'll go online and check

26:23.640 --> 26:25.570
if there's any other information.

26:27.500 --> 26:28.360
Make some room.

26:29.890 --> 26:33.350
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

26:36.700 --> 26:39.120
[Console]

26:39.340 --> 26:40.860
You know how to do this?

26:40.890 --> 26:41.870
This is called web scraping.

26:41.870 --> 26:43.790
It automatically gathers
publicly available information online,

26:43.790 --> 26:44.920
like the school website

26:44.920 --> 26:46.480
and videos posted by
student organizations.

26:46.480 --> 26:48.770
Since they're public,
accessing them is completely legal.

26:48.770 --> 26:50.680
[Console]

26:50.780 --> 26:52.110
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

26:57.030 --> 26:58.240
Will this really work?

26:58.240 --> 27:00.270
I could finish a dungeon by now.

27:01.200 --> 27:03.930
With your poor skills,
you'd be dead in 3 minutes.

27:08.660 --> 27:09.460
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

27:09.480 --> 27:10.250
[Visited and Extended Warm Greetings
to Overseas Students in the UK]

27:13.250 --> 27:14.330
Gather around.

27:15.640 --> 27:16.970
It's nice to see you all.

27:17.800 --> 27:19.710
We'll need you to attend
tomorrow's seminar.

27:17.890 --> 27:19.810
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

27:19.830 --> 27:21.620
[Visited and Extended Warm Greetings
to Overseas Students in the UK]

27:20.440 --> 27:21.000
Okay.

27:21.000 --> 27:21.750
And

27:22.060 --> 27:23.620
if possible, please share

27:23.650 --> 27:26.910
your experiences studying abroad
over the past few years.

27:27.880 --> 27:28.930
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

27:28.950 --> 27:30.160
[Visited and Extended Warm Greetings
to Overseas Students in the UK]

27:32.480 --> 27:32.990
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

27:33.010 --> 27:33.690
[Visited and Extended Warm Greetings
to Overseas Students in the UK]

27:38.030 --> 27:40.870
That gesture was exactly the same
as the one in the surveillance footage.

27:40.870 --> 27:42.800
This should be solid proof, right?

27:46.730 --> 27:48.140
Whether we can be absolutely certain

27:48.140 --> 27:50.960
still depends on
the police's further investigation.

27:50.960 --> 27:52.900
Tomorrow, we'll take all of this
to the police station

27:52.900 --> 27:54.920
and see if the evidence is sufficient.

27:54.920 --> 27:57.370
Think about it, he was actually able to
impersonate Ms. Lin.

27:57.370 --> 27:59.360
Who knows what other
disgusting things he might be hiding?

27:59.360 --> 28:00.720
Like clothes he's worn

28:00.740 --> 28:01.740
or wigs he's used.

28:01.810 --> 28:03.510
If he really has this kind of fetish,

28:03.510 --> 28:04.700
finding those items would prove

28:04.700 --> 28:06.950
that he had been deliberately
imitating Ms. Lin for a long time.

28:06.950 --> 28:07.670
No.

28:07.700 --> 28:08.790
He's too dangerous.

28:08.790 --> 28:09.880
You must not approach him.

28:09.880 --> 28:10.550
But...

28:13.230 --> 28:13.990
Understood.

28:14.340 --> 28:14.970
Let's eat.

28:19.050 --> 28:20.290
Alright. Let's eat.

28:31.790 --> 28:32.680
Ms. Lin.

28:32.880 --> 28:34.160
I think I had too much bubble tea.

28:34.160 --> 28:34.890
My stomach hurts a little.

28:34.890 --> 28:35.920
I need to use the restroom.

28:35.920 --> 28:36.530
Are you okay?

28:36.530 --> 28:37.790
I'm okay. Don't worry.

29:10.850 --> 29:12.000
What was that about?

29:19.900 --> 29:21.000
[Leippya Counseling Services]

29:20.040 --> 29:21.170
Xiang Zi's address?

29:21.290 --> 29:22.550
You actually found it.

29:24.160 --> 29:25.750
Villains die from talking too much,

29:25.750 --> 29:26.480
while heroes

29:26.920 --> 29:28.000
win by pulling surprise attacks.

29:28.000 --> 29:28.600
Surpri...

29:29.680 --> 29:31.750
You're going to Xiang Zi's place
to collect evidence?

29:31.750 --> 29:33.270
Sneaky. That's really sneaky of you.

29:33.270 --> 29:33.790
No.

29:33.790 --> 29:34.840
It's way too dangerous.

29:34.840 --> 29:35.400
It's okay.

29:35.400 --> 29:36.560
Qin Ao and I can handle it.

29:36.560 --> 29:37.860
You have something more important to do:

29:37.860 --> 29:39.050
keep Ms. Lin occupied.

29:39.050 --> 29:39.770
That's right.

29:39.770 --> 29:42.630
You must not let them find out
what we're going to do.

29:43.480 --> 29:44.270
Okay then.

29:45.480 --> 29:46.030
Let's go.

29:46.030 --> 29:46.560
Let's go.

29:46.720 --> 29:48.000
Share your location with me at all times.

29:48.000 --> 29:48.400
Okay.

29:48.680 --> 29:49.210
Bye-bye.

29:54.920 --> 29:55.920
This is the place.

29:56.910 --> 29:58.450
How do we get up there?

29:58.640 --> 30:00.750
Okay, then let's take Lulu along.

30:00.750 --> 30:01.270
Okay.

30:01.350 --> 30:02.680
We'll sneak in with them.

30:02.680 --> 30:03.790
Once we're up, I'll distract him,

30:03.790 --> 30:05.450
and you look for the evidence.

30:13.240 --> 30:14.110
Who are you?

30:14.110 --> 30:15.640
Ma'am, we just moved in.

30:15.960 --> 30:17.580
Let me hold it. Let me.

30:17.730 --> 30:18.380
Thanks.

30:20.440 --> 30:22.160
What do you want to have for dinner?

30:22.160 --> 30:23.490
How about pig trotters?

30:33.960 --> 30:34.880
This is it.

30:49.170 --> 30:50.500
Who are you looking for?

30:50.590 --> 30:51.680
We're here to see you,

30:51.680 --> 30:52.720
Mr. Xiang Zi.

30:53.480 --> 30:54.440
Who are you?

30:55.770 --> 30:57.550
We are Ms. Lin Wanxing's students.

30:57.550 --> 30:58.550
We're here to ask you

30:58.550 --> 31:00.480
something about her college days.

31:08.300 --> 31:09.260
Mr. Xiang Zi.

31:10.550 --> 31:11.680
Did she send you here?

31:11.680 --> 31:12.790
No, no.

31:13.320 --> 31:15.370
Ms. Lin told us
not to get involved in her affairs.

31:15.370 --> 31:17.200
But we didn't want to just
watch her be falsely accused,

31:17.200 --> 31:18.640
so we secretly took her college roster

31:18.640 --> 31:20.000
and wanted to help her
investigate them one by one

31:20.000 --> 31:21.260
to help clear her name.

31:21.720 --> 31:22.520
That's right.

31:23.350 --> 31:24.590
M-Mr. Xiang Zi.

31:24.960 --> 31:26.680
You're Ms. Lin's senior.

31:26.680 --> 31:27.920
Classmates would surely

31:27.920 --> 31:29.320
be willing to help each other,

31:29.320 --> 31:29.880
right?

31:35.200 --> 31:35.960
Come on in.

31:36.680 --> 31:37.550
Here are the slippers.

31:37.550 --> 31:38.880
Thank you, Mr. Xiang Zi.

31:41.420 --> 31:42.580
Keep the door open.

31:49.090 --> 31:51.290
Did your teacher ever mention me to you?

31:51.720 --> 31:52.720
Ms. Lin never mentioned

31:52.720 --> 31:55.500
anything about her time
at Yongchuan University.

31:55.500 --> 31:56.350
I see.

31:56.790 --> 31:58.070
I actually also want to know

31:58.070 --> 31:59.670
how she's been doing lately.

31:59.720 --> 32:00.270
Come on.

32:00.720 --> 32:01.410
Have a seat.

32:01.480 --> 32:02.940
I'll go get you some water.

32:23.680 --> 32:25.210
How's your revision going?

32:28.330 --> 32:29.200
N-Not bad.

32:29.880 --> 32:31.680
I'm working on irregular verbs.

32:33.140 --> 32:34.600
Is something on your mind?

32:37.720 --> 32:40.320
Actually, I've been thinking about
the match.

32:45.830 --> 32:48.090
Did Qin Ao and Wen Chengye really go home?

32:55.560 --> 32:57.670
They suddenly got into an argument,

32:57.690 --> 32:59.110
and then they had a falling-out.

32:59.110 --> 33:00.770
They both went home afterward.

33:00.770 --> 33:02.090
Fu Xinshu.

33:02.120 --> 33:03.080
You're lying.

33:03.980 --> 33:05.770
When you answered that question,

33:05.770 --> 33:08.010
your pupils shifted toward
the upper right.

33:08.010 --> 33:11.670
That's a typical response
associated with fabricated memories.

33:14.170 --> 33:14.960
Fu Xinshu.

33:15.920 --> 33:17.850
Where did Wen Chengye and Qin Ao go?

33:18.350 --> 33:19.480
I really don't know.

33:19.500 --> 33:20.580
Tell me the truth.

33:20.610 --> 33:22.370
Did they go see Xiang Zi?

33:32.180 --> 33:33.310
My stomach is upset.

33:34.310 --> 33:35.240
Have some water.

33:36.120 --> 33:37.170
Mr. Xiang Zi.

33:37.320 --> 33:38.780
My stomach hurts really bad.

33:38.780 --> 33:40.040
Where is the bathroom?

33:40.190 --> 33:40.930
On the second floor.

33:40.930 --> 33:41.520
This way.

33:41.770 --> 33:42.850
Okay, thank you.

33:45.640 --> 33:46.270
Thank you.

34:05.030 --> 34:06.440
How's your teacher

34:06.440 --> 34:07.640
been doing recently?

34:07.720 --> 34:09.000
Someone maliciously spread rumors

34:09.000 --> 34:10.659
about her on the school forum.

34:11.840 --> 34:12.630
She...

34:13.280 --> 34:14.260
She broke down

34:14.290 --> 34:15.690
and left for a while.

34:23.940 --> 34:24.710
But

34:25.060 --> 34:27.060
our coach already brought her back.

34:28.290 --> 34:29.730
Wang Fa brought her back?

34:30.179 --> 34:31.739
You know our coach's name?

34:31.770 --> 34:34.030
Then you must be quite close to Ms. Lin...

34:34.510 --> 34:35.159
It's okay.

34:35.190 --> 34:37.190
-I'm sorry. I really am.
-It's okay.

34:38.330 --> 34:39.730
I'm really sorry.

34:40.030 --> 34:41.000
It's okay.

34:41.000 --> 34:42.560
I'm really sorry.

34:58.840 --> 35:01.880
Ms. Lin and I were taught

35:01.880 --> 35:03.800
by the same professor.

35:05.870 --> 35:07.870
How has she been after she came back?

35:09.230 --> 35:10.070
She...

35:10.510 --> 35:12.890
Her condition even worsened
after she came back.

35:12.890 --> 35:14.920
A lot of people at school
have been spreading rumors about her,

35:14.920 --> 35:17.070
and she's been crying almost every day.

35:17.070 --> 35:17.800
Is that so?

35:19.110 --> 35:20.910
She's not the type to cry easily.

35:21.050 --> 35:22.580
It seems that this incident

35:22.920 --> 35:24.720
must have been a huge blow to her.

35:39.320 --> 35:40.360
Mr. Xiang Zi.

35:40.590 --> 35:41.880
Do you have any information or leads

35:41.880 --> 35:43.000
about Ms. Lin being falsely accused

35:43.000 --> 35:44.280
at school?

35:45.640 --> 35:47.570
I don't have any particular leads.

35:47.790 --> 35:49.190
She was falsely accused?

35:49.240 --> 35:49.990
Of course.

35:50.590 --> 35:53.770
I heard about
what happened to Ms. Lin before—

35:53.990 --> 35:56.520
that incident you called
a false accusation.

35:57.110 --> 35:58.360
If I remember correctly,
they said back then

35:58.360 --> 36:00.150
that the evidence was sufficient,

36:00.150 --> 36:02.410
so the school didn't intervene too much.

36:02.590 --> 36:03.630
That's all I know.

36:06.360 --> 36:07.230
Qin!

36:07.230 --> 36:08.360
Are you done shitting?

36:08.360 --> 36:09.110
Qin Ao?

36:14.230 --> 36:15.150
Qin Ao!

36:16.690 --> 36:17.510
Mr. Xiang Zi.

36:17.510 --> 36:18.070
I'll go.

36:21.340 --> 36:22.540
Mr. Xiang Zi, I'll go.

36:25.710 --> 36:26.760
Mr. Xiang Zi! Mr. Xiang Zi!

36:26.760 --> 36:27.820
What are you doing?

36:32.240 --> 36:33.340
What are you filming?

36:33.340 --> 36:34.290
Give me your phone!

36:34.290 --> 36:34.920
It was nothing, Mr. Xiang Zi.

36:34.920 --> 36:35.320
Give me the phone!

36:35.320 --> 36:36.030
It was nothing, Mr. Xiang Zi.

36:36.030 --> 36:36.930
-Run!
-Give me the phone!

36:36.930 --> 36:38.160
Qin, stall him!

36:38.630 --> 36:39.320
Get back here!

36:39.320 --> 36:39.800
Give me the phone!

36:39.800 --> 36:40.230
Run!

36:40.230 --> 36:40.760
Get back here!

36:40.760 --> 36:41.480
Run!

36:41.500 --> 36:42.400
Let me go!

36:44.550 --> 36:45.550
I won't let go no matter what!

36:45.550 --> 36:46.280
Let go!

36:46.280 --> 36:47.150
Let go!

36:47.150 --> 36:47.880
Let me go!

36:59.280 --> 37:00.400
Give me the phone!

37:00.400 --> 37:01.530
Don't give it to him!

37:01.710 --> 37:03.440
I won't give it to you no matter what!

37:03.440 --> 37:04.230
The phone!

37:04.230 --> 37:04.550
Qin!

37:04.550 --> 37:05.440
-Give me the phone!
-Hold him down!

37:05.440 --> 37:06.440
Give me the phone!

37:06.760 --> 37:07.760
I am holding him!

37:07.760 --> 37:08.670
Give me the phone!

37:08.670 --> 37:09.190
I am holding him!

37:09.190 --> 37:09.920
Give it to me!

37:10.190 --> 37:11.030
Coach.

37:11.440 --> 37:12.760
Ms. Lin.

37:12.760 --> 37:14.550
We took pictures of the clothes and wig

37:14.550 --> 37:15.710
he used to impersonate you.

37:15.710 --> 37:16.920
Since we found out his dark secret,

37:16.920 --> 37:18.000
he wouldn't let us leave.

37:18.000 --> 37:19.710
So you two were indeed sent by her.

37:19.710 --> 37:21.360
Is a loose woman like her

37:21.360 --> 37:23.020
really worth all your effort?

37:23.480 --> 37:24.360
I dare you to say that again!

37:24.360 --> 37:25.000
Come on.

37:25.110 --> 37:25.880
Beat me to death!

37:25.880 --> 37:26.960
Beat me to death! Come on!

37:26.960 --> 37:27.710
Stop!

37:28.670 --> 37:30.110
Let me talk to him in private.

37:30.110 --> 37:30.880
No!

37:31.420 --> 37:32.340
Don't worry.

37:47.710 --> 37:49.280
It's just the two of us now.

37:50.230 --> 37:52.560
There's no need to keep up the act
anymore.

37:53.630 --> 37:54.800
You impersonated me

37:55.550 --> 37:56.710
and deliberately let
the surveillance camera

37:56.710 --> 37:59.440
capture you
going into Professor Shu Yong's room

37:59.920 --> 38:01.710
just to slander and frame me.

38:02.920 --> 38:04.400
What did I ever do to you?

38:06.190 --> 38:07.150
Lin Wanxing,

38:09.070 --> 38:10.400
turn off the recording.

38:11.630 --> 38:12.710
I know

38:13.400 --> 38:16.060
you're just trying to
trick me into confessing.

38:19.460 --> 38:20.140
[Recording]

38:20.160 --> 38:21.520
[Recorder]

38:26.970 --> 38:27.900
You can talk now.

38:35.040 --> 38:36.330
I framed you?

38:37.320 --> 38:38.360
Lin Wanxing.

38:39.480 --> 38:41.480
I was only upholding my own justice.

38:44.800 --> 38:45.960
You ruined me,

38:46.530 --> 38:48.780
so of course I had to make you pay.

38:48.810 --> 38:50.530
What nonsense are you talking about?

38:50.530 --> 38:51.610
I ruined you?

38:52.230 --> 38:53.290
Playing dumb, huh?

38:53.400 --> 38:54.760
Weren't you the one who kept sending me

38:54.760 --> 38:55.820
flirtatious signals?

38:55.820 --> 38:56.650
Xiang Zi,

38:56.880 --> 38:58.440
stop flattering yourself.

39:03.050 --> 39:04.490
Me flattering myself?

39:05.050 --> 39:06.530
Me flattering myself?

39:06.850 --> 39:08.450
Once could be wishful thinking,

39:08.450 --> 39:10.040
but was it really the case
every single time?

39:10.040 --> 39:10.880
Lin Wanxing,

39:11.710 --> 39:13.490
you haven't changed at all—

39:13.510 --> 39:15.440
you dare to do it but not own up to it.

39:18.740 --> 39:20.050
Why would I admit to

39:20.760 --> 39:22.020
something I never did?

39:22.540 --> 39:24.270
Just because I turned you down,

39:24.380 --> 39:25.980
you held a grudge against me,

39:26.070 --> 39:27.800
and you dragged so many innocent people
to their deaths?

39:27.800 --> 39:29.200
Was it me?

39:29.220 --> 39:30.610
It was you, okay?

39:35.880 --> 39:36.710
Lin Wanxing.

39:38.290 --> 39:40.690
Aren't you curious about
how Shu Yong died?

39:41.100 --> 39:42.780
I'll tell you right now.

39:44.040 --> 39:45.710
Remember the day I tried to
give you the butterfly specimen,

39:45.710 --> 39:47.910
but you wouldn't take it no matter what?

39:47.960 --> 39:48.650
Right,

39:49.360 --> 39:50.630
it was also the day Shu Yong

39:50.630 --> 39:52.560
gave you the recommendation spot.

39:56.040 --> 39:56.830
Xiang Zi,

39:57.040 --> 39:58.500
is there anything urgent?

39:58.880 --> 40:00.010
I need to talk to you.

40:07.580 --> 40:09.710
It's about the recommendation spot,
isn't it?

40:09.710 --> 40:10.920
Do you have any idea how hard

40:10.920 --> 40:12.180
I worked for this spot?

40:12.180 --> 40:13.790
Why did it go to Lin Wanxing in the end?

40:13.790 --> 40:14.880
How is she better than me?

40:14.880 --> 40:17.410
Is it just because
her father is the director?

40:20.840 --> 40:21.800
Xiang Zi.

40:22.510 --> 40:24.140
Recommendation selections

40:24.170 --> 40:25.900
evaluate research competence,

40:25.900 --> 40:27.010
academic achievements,

40:27.010 --> 40:28.280
and long-term potential

40:28.280 --> 40:29.880
comprehensively.

40:30.910 --> 40:32.880
Lin Wanxing truly stands out

40:32.900 --> 40:34.630
in all these aspects.

40:36.030 --> 40:37.230
Stands out?

40:37.600 --> 40:39.120
In what way?

40:39.150 --> 40:41.070
She's nothing but a flirt.

40:42.280 --> 40:44.180
I don't want to hear

40:44.210 --> 40:45.920
such baseless rumors anymore.

40:45.920 --> 40:46.730
Xiang Zi.

40:46.750 --> 40:47.980
You should know

40:48.040 --> 40:49.640
that integrity is paramount

40:51.100 --> 40:52.910
in academia.

41:00.260 --> 41:01.520
What are you implying?

41:05.040 --> 41:06.690
Are your thesis data

41:07.360 --> 41:09.120
100% authentic?

41:17.020 --> 41:19.350
I'll never grant the recommendation spot

41:19.640 --> 41:22.040
to someone guilty of academic misconduct.

41:32.200 --> 41:33.410
Professor.

41:34.510 --> 41:36.590
Are you saying that in academia,

41:38.100 --> 41:39.850
integrity comes first?

41:40.500 --> 41:41.140
Yes.

41:45.230 --> 41:47.320
Well, if that's the case...

41:53.310 --> 41:55.230
Physicians cannot heal themselves.

41:55.230 --> 41:59.010
[Sertraline Hydrochloride Tablets]

42:01.380 --> 42:02.480
Professor.

42:03.600 --> 42:05.890
Your mental state has been

42:26.100 --> 42:27.500
rather unstable lately.

42:28.360 --> 42:29.190
Get out!

42:35.120 --> 42:38.210
As the most authoritative mentor
in psychology,

42:36.730 --> 42:44.480
[Certificate of Honor]

42:38.510 --> 42:40.510
can you truly call yourself honest?

42:41.190 --> 42:43.630
Would you dare let me
look into your paper

42:43.630 --> 42:44.630
from 20 years ago?

42:46.340 --> 42:50.000
[Certificate of Honor]

42:48.800 --> 42:50.630
You built your reputation
as a leading expert

42:50.630 --> 42:53.090
in this field
through academic misconduct.

42:56.180 --> 42:57.580
Where is your integrity?

42:59.230 --> 43:00.710
How did you find out?

43:04.470 --> 43:05.670
I happened to

43:06.960 --> 43:08.360
pick a research topic

43:08.760 --> 43:10.630
similar to yours,

43:10.680 --> 43:12.390
so I thoroughly looked into

43:12.410 --> 43:14.180
your profile

43:14.200 --> 43:17.310
and studied every single paper
you have published.

43:17.360 --> 43:19.800
I told you, I'm a very hardworking person.

43:20.070 --> 43:20.990
Professor.

43:21.480 --> 43:23.210
Surely you understand that

43:23.240 --> 43:24.280
every action

43:24.840 --> 43:26.510
leaves traces behind.

43:32.940 --> 43:34.580
Back during your postdoctoral research,

43:34.580 --> 43:36.080
you hit a wall

43:36.340 --> 43:37.960
and desperately needed published papers.

43:37.960 --> 43:39.970
If I hadn't chanced upon

43:39.990 --> 43:42.220
a relevant thesis,

43:42.340 --> 43:44.540
I might never have discovered

43:45.040 --> 43:47.570
that a set of experimental data
you published

43:47.960 --> 43:49.960
was plagiarized from someone else.

43:59.440 --> 44:01.900
Give me Lin Wanxing's recommendation spot,

44:02.430 --> 44:04.590
and I'll keep this secret for you.

44:05.690 --> 44:06.890
What do you say?

44:10.910 --> 44:12.910
You only have 3 days.

44:52.560 --> 44:53.500
-Hello, Professor.
-Hello, Professor.

44:53.500 --> 44:54.230
Hello.

44:56.890 --> 44:58.750
-Professor.
-Hello, Professor.

45:01.810 --> 45:02.930
Hello, Professor.

45:06.100 --> 45:07.250
Professor Shu.

45:07.940 --> 45:09.400
Have you made up your mind?

45:11.630 --> 45:13.330
A reminder—

45:13.800 --> 45:15.470
you've only got 2 days left.
